<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>Privacy Policy</h2>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="card shadow">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4>Data Collection and Usage</h4>
                <p>This inventory management system collects and stores the following types of data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>User account information (name, email, role)</li>
                    <li>Product information and inventory data</li>
                    <li>Customer and supplier information</li>
                    <li>Purchase and sales order data</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h4>Data Security</h4>
                <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Password encryption using BCrypt</li>
                    <li>Secure database connections</li>
                    <li>Role-based access control</li>
                    <li>Session management</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h4>Data Retention</h4>
                <p>Data is retained for as long as necessary to provide the inventory management services and comply with legal obligations.</p>
                
                <h4>Contact Information</h4>
                <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact the system administrator.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
